You stand in front of the Sarnath nightclub: The church of starry wisdom.
This ancient and impressive church is constructed completely of grey stone,
with intimidating gargoyles leering down from above. You can see the old tower
of the church to your right. There is a large archway with two immense doors
leading into the depths of Sarnath. This side of the old church throbs with an
eerie crimson glow... Partiers of BatCity are flowing up and down the stairs. 
The nightclub seems to be pulsing with activity tonight.

You are in the vestibule of Sarnath.
This is the narthex of the original church. Or it was. The vestibule is a
large room, with high peaked ceilings. It is lit by dozens of candles.
Psychedelic wheels of color swirl on the walls and on the high ceiling.
Frequent alcoves in the walls contain bizarre exhibits such as: severed heads
in jars, occult paraphenalia, warped and very weird looking mirrors, exotic
medical instruments, and a wide array of sexual fetish gear. Some of the stone
gargoyles have been dressed with the wild and kinky gear. The main entrance
opens directly to the nave. It is flanked by a pair of marble statues, an
angel and a succubus.
